Subject: Will it Sphere-ify - Sign Up Errata
Description: Spherification is a technique that transforms liquids into solid, edible spheres. People can use this technique to add color, texture, and flavor to their dishes. Join me as I experiment with spherification and try out a bunch of different liquids and see, WILL IT SPHERIFY? Space is limited, please sign up in advance near Ops!  Speakers include:Frannie - Track: Food  - Duration: 1 hour
